rows.label: tlk70000051_03_msg0001
rows.name:
You know, I don't have kids.
I'm not even married.

rows.label: tlk70000051_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Can you imagine me giving out fatherly
advice to anyone? "Sorry, no idea.
You're on your own with this one."

rows.label: tlk70000051_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I feel sorry for whatever poor sod has
to resort to asking me for advice. They
must be really scraping the barrel.

rows.label: tlk70000051_03_msg0004
rows.name:
If it was Mars having difficulties,
then I suppose I'd just try my best.
Even if it was some kinda kid problem.
